        <div n="506-14W2">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">WHO HAD BEEN MUCH ABUSED IN MANY INVETERATE LIBELS.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-506-14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-1" n="1">T<hi rend="small-caps">HE</hi> greatest monarch may be stabb'd by night,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-2" n="2">And fortune help the murderer in his flight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-3" n="3">The vilest ruffian may commit a rape,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-4" n="4">Yet safe from injured innocence escape;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-5" n="5">And calumny, by working under ground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-6" n="6">Can, unrevenged, the greatest merit wound.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-7" n="7">What's to be done? Shall wit and learning choose</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-8" n="8">To live obscure, and have no fame to lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-9" n="9">By Censure frighted out of Honour's road,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-10" n="10">Nor dare to use the gifts by Heaven bestow'd?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-11" n="11">Or fearless enter in through Virtue's gate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-14W2-line-12" n="12">And buy distinction at the dearest rate.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
